data.description: Experience the allure of this beautiful 4-bed, 3-bath split-level home just 20 minutes from downtown Atlanta. Chic and contemporary design meets functionality with an open chef's kitchen featuring stunning quartz countertops and a view to the family room. Enjoy spacious bedrooms, including a main-level primary suite and another primary suite on the lower level. No HOA or rental restrictions provide flexibility. Nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac, this residence is conveniently near schools, shopping, and restaurants. The oversized private backyard sets the stage for unforgettable entertaining experiences.
